<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN309-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇai – tumpai; tuṟai – nūḻilāṭṭu. maturaiyiḷaṅkaṇṇikaucikaṉār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN309">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>irumpumukañ citaiya nūṟi yoṉṉā</l>
<l>riruñcamaṅ kaṭatta lēṉōrkku meḷitē</l>
<l>nallarā vuṟaiyum puṟṟam pōlavuṅ</l>
<l>kollēṟu tiritaru maṉṟam pōlavu</l>
<l>māṟṟarun tuppiṉ māṟṟōr pācaṟai</l>
<l>yuḷaṉeṉa verūu mōroḷi</l>
<l>valaṉuyar neṭuvē leṉṉai kaṇṇatē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Demolishing [and] vanquishing the enemies in great battle </l>
<l>so that [his weapon’s] iron mouth is ruined, is easy for anyone.</l>
<l>Like the anthill in which a cobra stays,</l>
<l>like the village common in which a murderous bull roams,</l>
<l>there is with my lord a unique bright victorious eminent long spear</l>
<l>that frightens the opponents with a vigour difficult to appease:</l>
<l>“he is in the war camp!”   </l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
